<abstract>
    <para>
        SUSE® offers a full stack for your container workloads. This best practice document describes how you can make use of this offerings
        for your installation of Digital Manufacturing Edge included with SAP Digital Manufacturing Cloud. The operations of SAP Digital Manufacturing Edge and/or SAP Digital Manufacturing Cloud are not covered in this document.
    </para>

